# Private Knowledge Base — Project Context

AI-powered personal knowledge operations system. Local-first Docker Compose MVP.

## Normative stack (do not substitute without ADR)

- Python 3.12+, FastAPI, Pydantic v2, SQLAlchemy 2.x, Alembic
- PostgreSQL + pgvector, Neo4j Community, Redis + Celery
- LangGraph, Next.js + TypeScript
- Structured JSON logs, OpenTelemetry-compatible tracing

## Current phase

**Phases 0–6 complete.** **Phase 7** (personal sources + connection UI) and **Phase 8** (agent layer) are active specification tracks.

- Phase 7: `docs/13-personal-source-connectors-supplement.md`, `docs/14-source-connection-ui-supplement.md`
- Phase 8: `docs/05-agent-architecture.md`, `docs/15-agent-implementation-plan.md`

Agent implementation rules: `docs/08-ai-development-contract.md` §3.3.

